{"tid":2438840,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–為何南杏比北杏更具毒性？","createTime":"2021-03-08T20:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T05:23:26.000Z","uid":38861,"like":79,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f79d5ca3cf49863db1d4d91bd4f8b28acd397f40","tid":2438840,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T20:28:39.000Z","msg":"全球約有2000種植物含有物質可揮發成為山埃氣體，南北杏就是其中的兩種。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qbbyYp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qbbyYp.jpg&h=8370bfac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南杏仁又稱之為甜杏仁(sweet apricot kernel)，而北杏仁則為苦杏仁(bitter apricot kernel)。<br />\n<br />\n相對上，南杏仁的毒性比北杏仁遠之為低。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）南北杏內含化學物質扁桃苷(Amygdalin)，以及能夠分解扁桃苷並釋放出山埃的酵素。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Pvr7it.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Pvr7it.jpg&h=ade3932f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在正常情況下，扁桃苷及能夠分解它的酵素就像是牛郎及織女一樣被分隔開兩地。<br />\n而當我們嘴嚼南北杏的時候，其內部結構便會有所破壞，酵素亦得以與扁桃苷接觸，並釋發出對人體有害的山埃物質;<br />\n與此同時，胃酸及腸道細菌亦有能力將扁桃苷分解成為山埃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）每克北杏仁大概含有26 &plusmn; 14 mg扁桃苷，而每克南杏仁則大概含有0.16 &plusmn; 0.09 mg扁桃苷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7ff0DB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7ff0DB.jpg&h=6f0b4e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基於北杏所含的扁桃苷比南杏為高，因此相對上北杏在體內釋放出的山埃亦會較多。<br />\n山埃能夠抑制細胞產生能源的機制，對於經常性需要使用能源的心臟及大腦尤其傷害為深。<br />\n<br />\n口服山埃致命量為0.56mg/體重kg，以一個重80 kg的暴力警察為例，他口服44.8mg山埃後便會中毒致死。<br />\n<br />\n每457克的扁桃苷約可釋出26克的山埃，以北杏每克含有40mg扁桃苷作計算的話，80 kg的暴力警察攝取多少克北杏便會中毒身亡呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=88b594fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=ccb1d584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://efsa.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.2903/j.efsa.2016.4424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fefsa.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.2903%2Fj.efsa.2016.4424&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=479e5d53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://efsa.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.2903/j.efsa.2016.4424</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/02772248.2015.1030667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F02772248.2015.1030667&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=7e5ca4cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/02772248.2015.1030667</a>"},{"pid":"6eb6b5a5d5be879038e67002baeba5cbe3ca8f9b","tid":2438840,"uid":38861,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T20:29:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong>更正:為何北杏比南杏更具毒性先正確</strong></span>"},{"pid":"bf19ed9f8e3d538669b54571bd39b2ddebd9acc0","tid":2438840,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike"